		<titleShort>Indoril member</titleShort>
		<baseDescription>[PAWN_nameDef] was a member of the Great House Indoril, the great house of Indoril Nerevar himself. Like most members of House Indoril, [PAWN_nameDef] firmly believes that Dunmer culture must be respected and preserved, even the less desirable parts of it.</baseDescription>
